Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香找出了他幼稚園時候畫的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是父親還活著的時候  一起去的地方的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多小島的話…果然還是瀨戶內海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:06.61,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,80)\fad(500,500)}因為大家一起走很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你懷疑這兩個地方會不會是同一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季節也很相近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子想不到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ぴんっとこねぇっすな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓  來端一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心是蜜柑慕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  謝謝小香親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是奶奶做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是試作品  吃完說說感想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分樂意！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  照片上的地方有頭緒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似的地方有很多呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他每逢休息就出去拍照  我也沒有逐一問清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我記得那次玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真的做得很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這個味道好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在玉響是不是正在心中飄蕩著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  特意要去拍的話則是拍不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早有預謀可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福好像都溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該用拍這張照片時的心境去拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話再說回來  這張裡面還真拍到了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得當時這裡一定被幸福所包圍著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小香親畫的這張畫裡有著什麼線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這塊大石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不覺得眼熟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒印象呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用啊…包括我在內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想去那個地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  能去嗎  話說到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超強力幫手…登場！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰說無論如何都想讓我來  我就請了打工的假來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒叫你呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提起今天要集體商量這件事時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就突然說「啊  好想來」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}真是的  別說了  我不是讓你別說的嘛  笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近很熟悉瀨戶內的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想了想  小啪那張照片上的地方到底是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…那麼…想到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  無論如何都想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下週日大家一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說想去但是去不去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下週日早上10點在車站前集合怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一天晚上記得要好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿方便走路的鞋子來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴禁遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  不要忘帶換洗的內衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…內衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  今天大家就一起出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  兩個人一起去郊遊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和平常的那些朋友們一起出門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  下次再和大家一起來坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說準備好了馬上趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親  有困難的話要對紀惠姐說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以依靠姐姐哦  我會用MAXPOWER來守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我越說越燃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了好多點心  你要多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～這是何等的治癒力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠我立刻就被萌得壞掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親真是強得不能再強的傳說了呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要去哪裡問了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是某個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小島啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個香味是…來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家快點  錯過這班電車的話下一班就要等到1小時10分鐘後了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間慢騰騰的了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親快看  是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換乘公車  快跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親  要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作了些曲奇啥的  現在吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  從這裡開始再加把油  出發嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親  背包重嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  要姐姐幫你拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許現在正和大家一起走著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經與父親一起走過的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是和大家一起去見父親似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒…  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  姐姐  是不是還要往上爬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要爬多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還要爬兩小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  如果在這裡回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠姐的形象就會在小香親的心裡留下巨大的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好上了  不就是兩小時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我薰…隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親  累了就和紀惠姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  要姐姐背你嗎？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不累  照顧你兩個小時綽綽有餘 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:18.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}兩小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了這裡就只剩一小時左右了  再加把油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}前方恐有塌方危險  請勿進入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在這吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又走錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  真是個安靜的好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白說走錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這休息再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從家帶來了三明治和湯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽特製的蔬菜燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我做的飯糰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吃個三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃蔬菜燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  多吃點喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親喜歡蔬菜燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  要是我也做蔬菜燒帶來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做蔬菜燒味的曲奇怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  好新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個醬汁好好吃  麻音親特製的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  番茄好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  佐代美姐姐  還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者該說  為了我們這事還真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我們來做這麼累人的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  雖然確實很累人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小啪的爸爸的那張舊照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不覺間已經成為大家的回憶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然記不起是在何時何地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我確實感受到了曾經那似乎裝滿了整顆心的  就像是要溢出來了一樣的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片喚回了大家就快要忘卻了的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  各自的回憶雖然都不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是會不由地覺得那珍貴而又令人懷念的風景就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家想去看看那照片上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  吃飽了就出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了  就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦  小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方居然有這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有像那張照片上能遠望的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我  小香親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與那張照片稍微有點不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  好像是不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  來這裡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成小啪親  辛苦沒有白費呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風的味道  還是第一次聞到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風的聲音也和小鎮上聽到的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪也許真的和爸爸來過這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也許
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與照片上的地方不同  但是有種和爸爸相見了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  那裡成為了我們新的回憶之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家都有帶內衣來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶是帶了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等公車的這段時間去個好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒  澡堂  還是和小香親一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平常都是和我一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了不行了不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是澤渡楓  這是我弟弟澤渡香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙佐代美  是小薰的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我做完事前  大家一起先在院子裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有爸爸和小香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有工作  在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓今天開始就叫小啪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和爸爸要玩什麼呢  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:38.57,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,200)\fad(500,500)}因為是那一日的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  小啪親是姐姐給命名的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來還真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事…大家來看這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這個超有趣瞬間系列到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我抓拍獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓拍獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯過任何一個決定性的瞬間的抓拍獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那秘訣究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那人的情況是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下快門的時候  最佳鏡頭總是不期而至
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說沒有秘訣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果愛好是拍照的話  也許能讓別人教你各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點上啊  貌似她還沒有到愛好的程度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她專注於…小型秘境研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型秘境？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就在很近的地方  但卻可以有種外出玩玩的感覺的秘境地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  雖然說得很可愛但是我不會上當的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是秘境吧  要爬兩小時或者四小時的山路的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…而且她現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在尋找第二候選地研究中哦  紀惠君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}啊啊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蛋糕真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  好幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…  您是澤渡楓小姐的母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是志保美理穗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  洗好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然Maestro也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片上的地方是哪裡我也沒問過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要等姐姐的調查結果出來後…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再一起去嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香親會不會在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可能還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…要不要去小學接他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張也是小楓拍的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候她比她爸爸都熟悉相機的用法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  焦距一下就調好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！  志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來找你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在看澤渡小姐和你爸爸拍的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸拍的照片  無論哪張都讓人感覺暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像把當時你爸爸的那種心情直接拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐的照片  則感覺讓人愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像笑容要從照片中溢出般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有澤渡小姐的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不由得有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如看看剛才洗好的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我都還沒看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  讓我看讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是週日和大家一起出去時拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被嘲笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有拍到玉響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  這張小香親好帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐總是非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都拍得不好…果然技術很差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用這樣安慰我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是安慰  因為我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些照片裡都確實地映出了努力拍攝的小楓的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如奶奶說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每張照片裡都有小楓的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你爸爸的照片裡 也有你爸爸的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心與心相互交融了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  澤渡小姐  稍微一起去散下步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看小楓緊張成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…奶奶  下次做糕點能讓我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那太好了  請一定來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了  試作品的蜜柑慕斯很好吃  是要做那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好要去做這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐  要一直將攝影喜歡下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  好的  那一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為偶爾也有那種為了拍好而努力過頭  最終討厭拍照的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術一直原地踏步  變得厭倦甚至很長時間沒有拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是某一次呆呆地看著天空  突然好想拍拍看那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就拍了天空的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時沒有多想  呆呆地拍下的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得是最有自己的感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就再一次喜歡上拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不想  呆呆地去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾這樣也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擅長發呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我們拍張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  抬著那裡  然後喊1…2…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  1…2…  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}好  要拍嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  照片並不是要拍給誰看的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該試試為了自己而去拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要硬來  想拍就拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於決定第二候選地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:22:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照慣例這不會公佈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次是能坐車坐到半路  秘境等級為C的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那是幾級啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體參加  實行日是…下個星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血色星期天嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行已被修改 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}於是  星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坐上來的話就要走著去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是究極的選擇…由做好覺悟的人開始上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不暈車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是車子本身是沒問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  多麼美妙的風景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這裡的話  接下來只需走…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  1…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了  大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  原來是指20分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2小時怎麼說都太扯了點呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.57,0:25:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎  小香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.34,0:25:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.51,0:25:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小香等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.47,0:25:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以四處亂跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像…扭到腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  還能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.93,0:25:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.30,0:25:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫人來比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.64,0:25:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  最好不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打個電話給附近的人試試
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的絕對推薦地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.82,0:25:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地讓您帶我們來真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.60,0:25:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.23,0:25:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  到了  絕妙的景致之地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.67,0:26:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是拍那張照片的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.84,0:26:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.04,0:26:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  Maestro
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.11,0:26:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.55,0:26:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  那張照片是在這裡拍下的？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.84,0:26:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.77,0:26:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼漂亮的地方…一定是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  暫時就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓  我來背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.37,0:26:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  那樣太不好意思了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.89,0:26:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.58,0:26:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.02,0:26:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不重
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓姐被背背  小楓姐被背背  小楓姐變孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小香真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去背小香親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.81,0:26:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心無力…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的大海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.58,0:26:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起拍張照怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:26:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.28,0:27:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.77,0:27:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這片海總覺得好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.45,0:27:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.52,0:27:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡  小香畫裡面的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.12,0:27:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日山？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫裡的那片黑色…那個不是石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.26,0:27:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個一定是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香是在爸爸的背上看到了那片風景的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.55,0:27:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…爸爸的背上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～是的  是的是的是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.40,0:28:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了小楓姐  見到爸爸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…見到了呢  和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.12,0:28:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道這裡是不是那照片上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能夠和大家一起來到這裡  
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.89,0:29:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多虧了爸爸留給我的相機和照片
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.83,0:29:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能直接見面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.95,0:29:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在照片中確實映出了…爸爸的心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.83,0:29:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是從此以後也會一成不變的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.54,0:29:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片果然很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.10,0:31:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇這裡的停車場的話  只要20秒鐘就能到山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.89,0:31:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.70,0:31:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
